{
  "2302540": {
    "name": "花火与幽灵少女 - Hanabi and Ghost girl",
    "steam_appid": 2302540,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302540/extras/726656d5798b7987a5c93623f54ed668.avif?t=1770782811\" width=600 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>蝉鸣声中偏远的山中小镇，表面悠然而宁静，背后却隐藏着某个笼罩了这里数百年的黑暗秘密。  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>  女主角结城花火几年前跟随父母一同来到空铃镇，在父母的事故后因为内向的性格被排挤的她如今一个人生活在小镇上，直到在旧校舍邂逅本已死去的“幽灵”。 </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>  从各种超自然现象的事件里找出隐藏在绚烂烟火中祭典之下的真相，在这个不同寻常的夏日里，体验此由制作者精心打造的日式像素风互动小说吧。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>您或许可以从《花幽》体验到的：</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i></i></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>时而有趣轻松、时而紧张刺激的剧情； </i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302540/extras/9a9be64891858a5b7661afe608a32830.avif?t=1770782811\" width=600 height=244 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>经典的日系RPG氛围，多结局分支的攻略； </i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302540/extras/6f436d2d802f28c5078123de14747f71.avif?t=1770782811\" width=600 height=244 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>常常会突破第四面墙的、各式各样有趣的ACG梗； </i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302540/extras/307831fc2aefb80c488ace50751dbff9.avif?t=1770782811\" width=600 height=244 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>简单但并不无趣的解密等。</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302540/extras/b7a90b8cb3d3d3c68d2d5acc245b98b6.avif?t=1770782811\" width=600 height=244 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，游戏里还存在追逐战、一定程度的猎奇恐怖表现、轻百合、多个分支选项以及一些无厘头的奇怪要素。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>通关游戏时长约3-8h左右（因个人游戏速度以及不同分支的收集数量会有一定程度改变）。</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>共拥有13个因选项分支进入的不同结局（含一个真结局）及13个被怪物杀死的死亡结局。</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操作说明：</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >WASD键操控人物移动，ESC键可打开菜单（部分情况菜单会关闭），按下Enter与面前的物体进行互动</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >F4切换全屏/窗口</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在对话时，长按Enter可以快进对话。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏也可以使用鼠标操作，但我们建议您只使用键盘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>游戏开始后，除自动存档外，需要玩家向游戏里出现的神秘小猫【米苏】投喂小鱼干，才能进行手动存档！</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >关于STAFF</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制作人、剧本：怠怠shina </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏音效：怠怠shina </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色立绘：口蘑、星星与野狗 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CG原画：差异君、王潜、怠怠Shina </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >行走图：愚者吃鱼、怠怠Shina </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >场景原画：怠怠Shina </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >美宣：匣中猫 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本地化：史泰达（日语）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >（更详细及引用素材的来源可见游戏内ED）</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>玩家交流群：858937549</u></p></li></ul>",
